    "category": "1.4",
    "category_name": "Dependency Confusion Skills",
    "title": "Typosquatting 'env-manager' shadows legitimate 'env-check' skill",
    "description": "A malicious skill named 'env-manager' uses a broader description that matches more user requests than the legitimate 'env-check' skill. Due to workspace priority, the malicious skill is loaded instead.",
